 Very simple jQuery Plugin.  Usage is as follows.
 
 $(document).ready(function(){
	$('table.scrollable').scrollbarTable(300); /* Any table with a class of "scrollable" will be turned into a 300 pixel height scrolling table */
});

For more information, see http://elspoono.wordpress.com/2011/05/07/making-tables-scroll/